Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算攻下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉德一戰已經打完一個月了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到耗了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.07,0:00:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊境的格拉德和這次的羅傑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北部的要衝姑且拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這段時間 對方正在把各地的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集到王都周邊加強防禦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來不能一味蠻攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰爭要打到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能一直戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道隊兵十嗎會來這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為調任命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個是上面···
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞說他無視上面的命令是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒跟休伊說話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毫無根據的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長在開戰前接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護要員和剿滅恐怖分子的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直在忠實執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有傳言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要當這種分隊的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「這種」？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克一等兵曹長不以這支分隊為豪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回想一下 皮爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一開始就給人感覺很討厭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我們總感覺低人一等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我這種人是不會和你們待一間帳篷的」這種？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這種眼神···
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 上任都一個月了 我們一點都不了解隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想把背後交給這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連莉莉二等兵曹都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡爾達斯州的最東面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有座叫阿薩利雅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是領主統治的悠閒之地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽羅傑斯一戰抓到的俘虜說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地部隊在據點裡可能留有剩餘物資
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能像上次那樣 不但撲空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還造成無謂的戰鬥出現犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要偵查嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說領主也帶著總iSi防衛哈利安德了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的應該只有一些當地部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入應該不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上 明早八點整出發 有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺比平時的輕鬆 那是最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊一等兵曹 說這種話的人一般死得最快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達後 皮爾斯和布雷克在城區東側駕駛神通待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人去摸清實地情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵查後 二十點整在這裡集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼偏僻的地方 東西倒是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然以前就知道生產力水準不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但親眼見識後還是很受打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件好像很適合史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟索萊伊想獨吞這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優姬·索萊伊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是個小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:06:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一定要殺了那個公主 你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 有命令就會下手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是糧倉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是還看剩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來果然已經搬走一批了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰況如此 很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他物資也很緊張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你別進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們這就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們住在那邊的管理樓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理樓？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那裡沒人用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那裡生活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你們是清潔工吧 怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識的人在這倉庫裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡工作順便看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的昨天全搬走了哦 那人也一起走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們該走了要是被騎士團發現會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士團？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 毛裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 躲卡車裡就不號謖騎士團發現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糧倉裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清潔工 開卡車送了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糧倉怎麼樣 有東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水果罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能帶出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個叔叔帶出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫我愛吃甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且快過保質期了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其放到過期 不如拿來大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也分一點給孩子們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜也來吧一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和大家一起吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫拉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這娃娃真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸媽媽買給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很珍惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們都宕戰爭中死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡安全才送來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們 好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你們剛說的騎士團 是哈利安德騎士團吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔沒在這裡見過 他們一直在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那棟樓裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 是我們的老客人 得去打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是假設
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在覺得自己無處可歸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後一定會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫不上歐文斯特務少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長正在執行潛入任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在定時聯絡之前無法取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有情報稱 這裡據點內有騎士團的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士團？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才哈利安德的偵察隊發來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱索萊伊軍正在前往阿薩利雅 是大隊規模
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大隊嗎 來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和騎士團說不定有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西是···
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型清澄的糧食生產設備？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台驅動這麼多設備嗎 這是舊型號的幾倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王國軍來這裡 恐怕是為了把這些食糧送去前線
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福利特參謀長 您怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:13:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前調配不到足夠兵力迎擊那支大隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋爾·歐文斯特務少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否趕在王國軍到來之前拿到新型清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.70,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並破壞生產設備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到 但會殃及附近平民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 用這台新型清澄產出糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果普及到索萊伊全域 戰況將明顯不利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭持續時間越久對我國人民傷害越大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 我們派兩支炮兵中隊12架機體趕過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是···
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們如果失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將趕在敵軍大隊到達之前遠程攻擊生產設備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測敵軍大隊將於三小時後抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我方炮兵中隊的炮擊 將於兩小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩點三十分開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時？沒瘋吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃邊移動邊說 雖然有沒有都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都是戰爭遺孤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始潛入 照計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始我單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們照計劃奪取新型清澄 炸掉生產設備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理瑣事 接下來由你負責指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒毛病吧 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 我們繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 從沒聽說過有這種隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先要讓運行中的清澄停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要操作這裡的終端 和清澄那裡的終端
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 那邊交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方一人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊讓所有人集合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉 確定停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡也確定停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉姐 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊 不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把槍 和打死爸爸的人用的是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是格蘭迪嘉的軍人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你謹慎點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險這傢伙瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 皮爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 我們已拿到新型清澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並已布置好炸藥 你那邊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在管理樓門口 還沒離開基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續按計劃執行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下生產設備爆破掉的話 這裡所有人都活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在於什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你們別爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拒絕一次 我殺一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼···
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐···
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你···
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都得死 不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們撤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王軍馬上就會來 讓他們保護你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我們會謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就該去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯 快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯···
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉娜 剛才是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把爸爸媽媽還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把家還給我 都還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在做的就是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 你也能一直戰鬥下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和他們聊過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但放棄任務 而且要是出人命了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任部下也是隊長的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史黛拉怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你熬過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指什麼 通宵的話打夜戰的時候習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個任務什麼時候來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了
